title: Lil Wayne Discography + Mixtape Albums + Mixtapes [RAP]
description:
My collection of Lil' Wayne Albums and all of his best mixtapes. I know DJs love to put out a new mixtape every week of the same old weezy tracks, my collection below are only mixtapes that showcased the newest Wayne tracks at the time. 

Enjoy.


DISCOGRAPHY:

Tha Block is Hot (1999)
Lights Out (2000)
500 Degreez (2002)
The Carter (2004)
The Carter II (2005) (+Bonus CD)
Like Father, Like Son (2006) (+Bonus CD)
